": \"3-3-onboard-alias\",\n      \"description\": \"**Test file size:** onboard.test.ts is 325 lines vs estimated 100-150. Consistent with project norms (audit.test.ts is 407 lines).\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-7\",\n      \"story\": \"3-3-onboard-alias\",\n      \"description\": \"**console.log in shared handler:** audit-action.ts line 107 uses console.log directly. Story says \\\"Do NOT use console.log directly\\\" but formatAuditHuman() returns pre-formatted strings — wrapping in ok()/info() would double-prefix.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-8\",\n      \"story\": \"3-3-onboard-alias\",\n      \"description\": \"**HIGH: Unsafe double type assertion** in audit-action.ts:86 — `as unknown as Record<string, unknown>` bypassed type safety. Fixed with spread operator.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-9\",\n      \"story\": \"3-3-onboard-alias\",\n      \"description\": \"**MEDIUM: Dead branch guard** in audit-action.ts:101 — `fixStories &&` always true at that point. Simplified to `else`.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-10\",\n      \"story\": \"3-3-onboard-alias\",\n      \"description\": \"**MEDIUM: NFR9 violation** — onboard.test.ts at 325 lines, compacted to 230.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-11\",\n      \"story\": \"3-3-onboard-alias\",\n      \"description\": \"**MEDIUM: Branch coverage gap** — missing test for `skipped: true` path. Added, now 100%.\",\n      \"source\": \"retro\",\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"migrated-12\",\n      \"story\": \"3-3-onboard-alias\",\n      \"description\": \"**LOW (not fixed): console.log in audit-action.ts:111** — established codebase pattern, needs new 