{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PmQQH9dkwiWNwb8QhGE37j","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Review Module\n     2→\n     3→Code review execution. Invokes BMAD code-review workflow via child_process and returns structured results.\n     4→\n     5→## Files\n     6→\n     7→- `index.ts` — Public API: `reviewStory(key, opts?)` — delegates to orchestrator, re-exports `ReviewResult` type. Only public interface for the module.\n     8→- `orchestrator.ts` — Workflow invocation: `invokeBmadCodeReview(key, opts?)` — spawns `claude --print` with BMAD code-review prompt, parses review output for approval/rejection signals, extracts comment lines. Handles timeout (killed/SIGTERM) and non-zero exit errors. Internal to module.\n     9→- `types.ts` — Module-specific types: `ReviewResult` (key, approved, comments, duration, output — all readonly)\n    10→\n    11→## Patterns\n    12→\n    13→- All public functions return `Result<T>` (never throw)\n    14→- Uses `execFileSync` for main workflow\n    15→- ES module imports with `.js` extensions\n    16→- Default timeout: 25 minutes (1,500,000ms)\n    17→- Output truncated to last 200 lines\n    18→- Approval detection uses heuristic keyword matching on review output\n    19→- Defaults to `approved: true` when no rejection signals detected\n    20→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01NPoMRLksRrYS1379XfDBqY","session_id":"7be24b04-34e1-424a-85e4-e656cce56dfe","uuid":"9a594fc0-f2d3-4c3d-8526-cef92ca08513","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:10:17.203Z"}
