{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01B7y7mgP8xLvryZWDsrULF7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01ChgVHTZDgwgvG7zp1voqzD","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- **Coverage: 96.98% overall, 2855 tests, all 121 files above 80% floor**\n\n","new_string":"- **Coverage: 96.98% overall, 2855 tests, all 121 files above 80% floor**\n\n### 5-1-code-review-observability-check — verify (2026-03-21T06:22Z)\n\n- **Infrastructure issue (fixed):** verify-env prepare does NOT copy patches/ into the Docker container. Container uses globally installed npm package (v0.23.1) which predates this story's changes. First verification run failed 5/6 ACs because patches were stale.\n- **Fix applied:** Manually copied updated patches into container via `docker cp`. Re-verification passed 6/6.\n- **Systemic concern:** Any story that modifies `patches/` will hit this same issue. The verify-env prepare or Docker image needs to include current patches, not just the published npm version.\n- **ACs #2-#4 verified via patch content + semgrep tooling** rather than live Claude agent sessions (Claude CLI wasn't authenticated in container). This is a reasonable proxy but not a full integration test.\n\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":158,"cache_read_input_tokens":75135,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":158},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7be24b04-34e1-424a-85e4-e656cce56dfe","uuid":"b055f638-1ae4-4948-98e7-1afd88b1d635"}
